data.description: Look at this 4-bedroom 2 bath pool home that is perfectly situated on .89 acres. The entire home has been updated and offers an open floor plan with a spacious open kitchen. A few updates include newer LPV wood flooring, crown molding, newer appliances and the roof was replaced in 2020. All secondary bedrooms are nice sized and offer spacious closets. Just off the interior laundry room is a screened lanai offering privacy and overlooks the yard and pool. The pool was completely redone and updated in 2018. The property is completely fenced and offers a 20 x 30 concrete pad perfect spot to park your boat/RV or both. Complete RV hook up available. The well house/shop has 220 power.  100% USDA financing available! No HOA! Convenient location close to shopping and SR 415 for an easy commute to Orlando and the Beaches. Call for more details!
